<li id="cite_note-26"><b><a href="#cite_ref-26" title="">^</a></b> These and other abbreviations are listed in Chao(1968a):xxx.</li>
<li id="cite_note-27"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27" title="">^</a></b> The rules are given, though in a different form, in Chao (1948): 28–30 (synopsis p 336) and Chao (1968a): 29–30 (synopsis p 847). See also Table IX in Simon, W.(1947):lviii.</li>
